filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT

CASE 

WHEN endgame.event_subtype_full = 'rules_engine_event' THEN 'AB'

WHEN endgame.event_subtype_full != 'rules_engine_event' THEN 'Threats'

END as \"Type\",

count(*) AS c 

FROM \"endgame-*\"

WHERE event.kind = 'event' AND endgame.event_subtype_full != 'diagnostic_event'

GROUP BY \"Type\""
| pointseries color="Type" size="max(c)"
| pie hole=67 labels=false legend=false palette={palette "#ffeda0" "#feb24c" "#f03b20" gradient=true} labelRadius=100 seriesStyle={seriesStyle label="Threats" color="#F13B1F"}
  seriesStyle={seriesStyle label="AB" color="#0088A7"}
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT 

CASE
WHEN endgame.event_subtype_full = 'file_classification_event' THEN 'Malware'
WHEN endgame.event_subtype_full = 'exploit_event' THEN 'Exploit Protection'
WHEN endgame.event_subtype_full = 'rules_engine_event' THEN 'Adversary Behavior'
WHEN endgame.event_subtype_full = 'kernel_shellcode_event' THEN 'Process Injection'
WHEN endgame.event_subtype_full = 'diagnostic_event' THEN 'Sensor Diagnostic'
WHEN endgame.event_subtype_full = 'cred_theft_event' THEN 'Credential Theft'
END as \"Alert Type\",

count(*) as c 
FROM \"endgame-*\"
WHERE event.kind = 'alert' AND endgame.event_subtype_full != 'diagnostic_event'

GROUP BY \"Alert Type\" 
ORDER BY c DESC
LIMIT 5"
| table 
  font={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=14 align="left" color="#FFFFFF" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false} showHeader=false
| render css=".canvasDataTable__tbody>:nth-child(odd) {
background-color: #323233;
}"

  query="SELECT
CASE 

WHEN host.os.name = 'Linux' THEN 'Linux'

WHEN host.os.name = 'macOS' THEN 'Mac'

WHEN host.os.name = 'Windows' THEN 'Windows'

GROUP BY \"OS\"
